canonical:
  title: 春帖子
  author: 姜碩德
  language: lzh
  text: 靑歸園菜嫰白放野梅新圭竇逢佳節瑤徽賀小春
  rtl: true
  vertical: true
lzh_formatted:
  title: 春帖子
  author: 姜碩德
  language: lzh
  text: 靑歸園菜嫰。白放野梅新。圭竇逢佳節。瑤徽賀小春。
korean:
  title: 춘첩자
  author: 강석덕
  language: kor
  text: |-
    푸른 빛은 원의 채소 싹에 돌아와 곱고
    흰 빛은 들매화를 피워 새로워라
    규두에 가절을 만나
    요휘(瑤徽)로 소춘을 하례하네
  url: https://db.itkc.or.kr/dir/item?itemId=BT#dir/node?dataId=ITKC_BT_1365A_0220_010_0640&viewSync=OT
  footnotes:
  - key: '[주-D001] 요휘(瑤徽) : '
    value: 거문고를 말하는데, 요주(瑤柱)에 줄[徽]을 매었다는 말이다.
english:
  title: Spring Tribute Poem
  author: Kang Seok-deok
  language: eng
  text: |-
    Green returns to the garden's tender shoots,
    White unfolds the wild plum's newborn bloom.
    Through the casement window meets the auspicious season,
    And the jade-strung zither sings praise to early spring.
  footnotes:
  - key: ''
    value: The 'jade-strung zither' (瑤徽) refers to a traditional Korean stringed instrument with strings attached to a jade bridge, used here as a poetic instrument of celebration and blessing.
